O'Reilly & Associates publishes two relevant books in their
"Nutshell" series; you probably want the first one.

                            List Price
Using UUCP and USENET       US$21.95
Managing UUCP and USENET    US$24.95

You should be able to find these at technical bookstores, or you
can order from uunet--send e-mail to uunet!orders for current
prices and ordering information.


